description: Access to the QE2 marina is being restricted due to the discovery of what is believed to be WW2 ordnance.
title: Guernsey WW2 ordnance found off east coast
title_page: Guernsey WW2 ordnance found off east coast - BBC News
maintext: "Unfortunately, those who wish to enter and leave the QE2 marina will be inconvenienced for a short time until the device has been removed.
